item.title: THIS THEME CAN BE USED LIKE A CORPORATE/BUSINESS THEME WITHOUT THE CART?
item.content:encoded:
Sure!
We included a lot of portfolio layouts and also a lot of different blog page, services page and so on. With 250+ shortcodes and a lot of different widgets you can create a great corporate theme, without any e-commerce feature.
Enjoy Bazar for your corporate/portfolio site!!

item.title: CAN I USE THIS THEME IN UNLIMITED DOMAINS?
item.content:encoded:
For the Themeforest rules, with the regular license you can use the theme only in 1 domain.
If you want to use the theme on 3 domains, for example, you have to purchase the theme 3 times. Or purchase the extended license so you can use the theme on unlimited domains ....and you will make me happy :)

item.title: CAN I USE THE THEME LIKE A CATALOG AND TURN OFF THE CART FEATURE?
item.content:encoded:
You can use the theme like a corporate theme, using the portfolio pages or the blog pages and also use the theme like a catalog.
If you install Woo Commerce, in the theme options panel you can easily turn off the cart on the header, the add to cart buttons and so on. In each product page you can turn on the "product enquiry" form if you want that the user have to contact you to know price or details for the product!

item.title: CAN I CREATE PRODUCT VARIATIONS LIKE SIZE, COLORS AND SO ON?
item.content:encoded:
Sure, you can create unlimited product variations. For each variation you can set a different price and also a different image.
Watch this great videotutorial to learn more about the product variations:
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_qOmOIxpjDw

item.title: CAN YOU PROVIDE INSTALLATION OR UPDATE SERVICE? I’M SO NEWBIE WITH WORDPRESS!
item.content:encoded: Sure, with a small fee of 39$ we can install Bazar on your WordPress installation. We will install Woo Commerce and import the sample data of our demo so you will have the same content and settings of our live preview!

item.title: Do you provide free support to setup this theme?
item.content:encoded: Sure. After the purchase you can access to our suppor forum and open a new topic if you need help from our developers. In the forum you can also watch a lot of videotutorials and also download our sample data to make your site like our demo with just 2 clicks!

item.title: I really like your demo. Can i import your xml file?
item.content:encoded: Yes, after the purchase you can access in our support forum and download the sample data of our demo. It's an .gz file that you can easily import in the "Import" panel of your theme and in 5 minutes you will have the same content and options of our live preview in your wordpress installation. Quick and easy!

item.title: I like the slider of the home #1 and the shortocodes of the home#7, can i mix the pages?
item.content:encoded: Sure. The home pages of our demo are just an example of what you can do using the sliders and the shortcodes availables in the theme. You can mix the elements and create your custom home page.

item.title: Tried to install the theme but i have a "style.css missing" issue!
item.content:encoded: Please, read the documentation. You are installing the wrong file. You have to upload the room09.zip archive, not the zip you downloaded from themeforest! Be sure you are installing the right file in your wordpress site.
